Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0090,,{\fad(400,400)\fs36\fnMSungHK-Bold\bord0\shad2}2024年3月6日 第56層 帕尼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.55,0:00:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把場地Boss誘進村子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.02,0:00:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.91,0:00:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼做的話村民會…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.72,0:00:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這正是我的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.35,0:00:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在Boss殘殺NPC的時候我們趁機攻擊Boss並將其殲滅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.50,0:00:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NPC不同於石頭和樹木這些建模
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.25,0:00:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.29,0:00:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是活著的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.56,0:00:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想這麼說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.00,0:00:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是單純的建模而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.26,0:00:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算被殺了也會重生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法順從你的意見
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.52,0:00:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此次作戰將由我——血盟騎士團副團長亞絲娜全權指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.88,0:00:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你聽從我的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.13,0:01:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 又起糾紛了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.65,0:01:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾基爾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.92,0:01:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和副團長小姐怎麼老是那樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.43,0:01:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必是我們性情不合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.40,0:01:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能變強的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.15,0:01:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以如果日後有某位值得你信賴的人邀請你加入公會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.71,0:01:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可不要拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.32,0:01:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是這麼對她說過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.96,0:01:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但沒想到她會成長為頂尖公會的攻略之鬼啊

Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.34,0:01:48.70,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}認めてた臆病な過去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:56.77,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}分からないままに怖がってた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.14,0:01:58.89,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}後ろの自分が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:05.72,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}現実を今に映す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.83,0:02:10.83,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}いくつもの空を描いた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.20,0:02:12.89,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}ここはきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.20,0:02:18.37,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}儚い心 乱して
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.59,0:02:24.08,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}夢で高く飛んだ躰は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.15,0:02:26.94,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}どんな不安纏っても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.10,0:02:28.98,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}振り払ってく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:33.42,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}眠る小さな想い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:35.64,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}広がりだして
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.82,0:02:37.70,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}気づく 弱い 私
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.84,0:02:44.40,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}君がいれば 暗い世界 強くいれた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.25,0:02:50.16,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}長い夢見る心は そう 永遠で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:54.27,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}I wanna always stay with you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:59.87,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}I give you everything I have

Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.34,0:01:48.70,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}正視著膽怯的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:56.77,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}依然無法理解地畏懼著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.14,0:01:58.89,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}背後的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:05.72,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}此刻映照在現實中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.83,0:02:10.83,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}描繪了數片天空的此處
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.20,0:02:12.89,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}一定是在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.20,0:02:18.37,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}亂我脆弱心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.59,0:02:24.08,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}乘著夢想高飛身軀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.15,0:02:26.94,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}無論有任何不安糾纏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.10,0:02:28.98,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}都掙脫前進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:33.42,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}將沉睡著的小小的心願
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:35.64,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}擴展開來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.82,0:02:37.70,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}意識到弱小的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.84,0:02:44.40,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}只要有你在 黑暗的世界 也能一直堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.25,0:02:50.16,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}用沉眠許久的心 永遠堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:54.27,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}I wanna always stay with you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:59.87,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}I give you everything I have

